The year is 2420.
The Solar System is at the same level of growth of the cancerous phenomennon 'humanity' as earth was around 2000 - all planets are colonized, all resources tapped into, all space used for garbage dumps, all the time used for lies and backstabbery
Machines are cheap, but huans - even more so.
Small 'science scout crafts' are the spores the desiese has sppred through the neighbouring Galaxies.
Those crafts often get stuck without oxigen, energy, food, water or spare parts and are subject to toretorous extinction.
Your are the captain of one such craft and taka control jsut after aheavy crash.
Enjoy!
